          "type": "copy",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You go to the water for clarity. To focus. To disconnect. But water never stays still. Wind shifts. Currents move. Your position drifts. And when your craft feels unsteady, so do you. Ventral changes that.</p>"
          }
        },
        "copy-2": {
          "type": "copy",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We design every vessel for greater control on the water. Intelligent systems help you manage your position in wind and current. Precision handling helps you stay where you want when the water won't.</p>"
